Description_lang: If you have a totem active, your totem grants you a shield absorbing ${$mhp*$s1/100} damage for $457387d every $457390d.

description_blz.en_US: If you have a totem active, your totem grants you a shield absorbing 11,840 damage for 30 sec every 30 sec.
